        "action": "Reduce Speculation & Derivatives",
        "additional_details": "1. Ban all short selling of currencies and securities.\r\n2. Ban all securitisation of loans, mortgages and derivatives, as well as all SPVs and SIVs.\r\n3. Ban all CDSs (credit default swaps).\r\n4. Ban all over the counter derivative trading. Allow only derivatives that are understood and approved by a regulatory agency, which are traded on an approved exchange.\r\n",
